long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Onet Connect Animal is a delightful and captivating game available as a Chrome extension. Dive into a world of adorable animals and engaging puzzle challenges. The goal of the game is to connect matching animal tiles with lines, but the catch is that the connecting lines cannot intersect or pass through other tiles. With limited moves and a race against the clock, you must strategize and plan your moves carefully to clear the board and advance to the next level. As you progress, the puzzles become more complex and challenging. 
The game features charming animal graphics, soothing music, and intuitive controls. Onet Connect Animal is a perfect choice for puzzle enthusiasts and animal lovers looking for a relaxing and enjoyable gaming experience. Connect the animals, test your memory, and have a great time exploring the captivating world of Onet Connect Animal on Chrome Extension.
